My new fave skirt 💛✨

I know this is my fashion page and my caption isn’t relevant to fashion and to all my fashion queens that follow me, however I feel I need to explain my lack of fashion posts or interest in doing so.. 

So Here goes……🥺

I’ve been quiet on here lately and those who’ve seen my stories probably know why.
What’s unfolding in Gaza — the genocide we’re witnessing in real time — has deeply affected me. I’ve felt heartbroken, helpless, and angry.

Angry at the world leaders doing nothing.
Heartbroken over the lives being lost.
Helpless watching innocent people — children, women, and men — being torn apart.

I just don’t have the headspace for fashion content right now. It doesn’t sit right with me while so many are suffering at the hands of Israel.

This is the painful reality.
What’s happening is shocking, inhumane, and deeply unjust.

Please don’t look away🇵🇸✊🏼

Im not giving up on my content at all and I am in the process of doing more “prancing around getting ready with dogs under my feet” so just bare with me my beautiful fashionistas ♥️
